column11:
@DavidHundeyin I'll certainly support scrapping of the NYSC scheme.

1.Introduce Small Buiness/Vocational Training as part of General Studies (GS)

2. Put together the over-inflated figures allocated for each 'corper' by the State for the 12-month period &amp; give them to students upon graduation.

